e: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n勿忘初衷，五大訴求！<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67ZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=410f8b73\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/vK4Dfno.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvK4Dfno.png&h=f4f33a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCDXv4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCDXv4t.jpg&h=c2140d08&s={SIZE}\" /> </div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4.追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>七區集會</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n  日期：8月5日<br />\n  時間：下午一時開始<br />\n各區地點：金鐘添馬公園、旺角麥花臣球場、沙田百步梯、大埔廣福球場、荃灣沙咀道球場、黃大仙廣場、屯門公園<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLCv36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLCv36.jpg&h=09ba4839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKejKpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKejKpu.jpg&h=f51b4d73&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ef22006887d50fdcba8055255d76a16d26756e62","tid":1380863,"uid":158090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:56:58.000Z","msg":"郭家麒: 暴力既源頭係林鄭政府，造成今日既亂局係有中央政府包庇林鄭同警隊 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1380805/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\